I made friends with a group of people that were consistantly on when I was on, and we keep a chat channel open all the time.   The results...never LFG.  It's like having a guild with no commitments <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
