Anyway, the suggestion to making as many friends as possible is a great one...that's the easiest way to ensure groups will be available to you.  Other than that, I have seen due to the population on this server, groups are usually on a BYO basis.  (bring your own!)<br>
<br>
We were the only ones in most of the midlevel zones so far, which can be good for us and getting camps we want....but bad for those that are LFG.  (most of us play at late hours too so that could be part of it...9pm pst to 3am pst usually)<br>
