<br>
Play what looks fun to you.  It's a game.  There are lots of 'group friendly' classes.  And all classes can add to a group.  Although there are a few classes that are less likely to be sought after in groups, most groups aren't formed that way.  Most groups are formed from friends that play together a lot, at the same times, in the same zones, that tend to mysteriously end up bouncing around the globe to similar zones and experiencing similar things ...<br>
<br>
The bottom line is to pick something that looks interesting and fun to you from 1 all the way to 50.  Then, get good at what you do, become a guru.  Make lots of friends by grouping, being skillful, and playing well. <br>
<br>
Groups are just a collection of individual people.<br>
<br>
Wyndaria, <br>
56 bard<br>
